NEWS/ChangeLog for bride
--------------------------------


version 1.2    2013-03026

    * changed variable names of variance estimates
      from "relv" to "rel.var"
    * updated the calculation of variance estimates
      (now according to http://arxiv.org/abs/1303.6182)
    * new method to avoid inconsistent estimators (e.g. rel<0)
      due to the bias correction (also according to arxiv paper)
    * removed cross table, binned probabilities from output
      variables


version 1.1    2013-03-11

    * initial release
